      "$value": "Geist",
      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "Universal type family — all headings, body, nav, buttons, cards, footer. The tight line-height (1.0–1.11) on display sizes and 700 weight creates a dense, confident display voice; 400 at 1.4 keeps body readable without feeling loose."
    }
  },
